{
    "$schema": "./pack-schema.json",
    "id": "azure_sdk_settings",
    "description": "Azure specific datasource fields from https://github.com/grafana/grafana-azure-sdk-go / https://github.com/grafana/grafana-azure-sdk-react. Field definitions mirror the controls rendered by the Azure Monitor `ConfigEditor` (composed of `MonitorConfig`, `AzureCredentialsForm`, `AppRegistrationCredentials` and `CurrentUserFallbackCredentials`). Storage shape mirrors the `AzureCredentials` discriminated union at `jsonData.azureCredentials` and the `AzureDataSourceSecureJsonData` keys.",
    "fields": [
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.authType",
            "key": "authType",
            "section": "azureCredentials",
            "label": "Authentication type",
            "description": "Choose the type of authentication to Azure services",
            "valueType": "string",
            "target": "jsonData",
            "role": "auth.discriminator",
            "defaultValue": "clientsecret",
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Discriminator for the `AzureCredentials` union stored at `jsonData.azureCredentials.authType`. Mirrors the `AzureAuthType` definition in `grafana-azure-sdk-react/src/credentials/AzureCredentials.ts`."
            },
            "validations": [
                {
                    "type": "allowedValues",
                    "values": [
                        "clientsecret",
                        "clientcertificate",
                        "msi",
                        "workloadidentity",
                        "currentuser",
                        "clientsecret-obo",
                        "ad-password"
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "ui": {
                "component": "select",
                "options": [
                    { "label": "App Registration (Client Secret)", "value": "clientsecret" },
                    { "label": "App Registration (Client Certificate)", "value": "clientcertificate" },
                    { "label": "Managed Identity", "value": "msi" },
                    { "label": "Workload Identity", "value": "workloadidentity" },
                    { "label": "Current User", "value": "currentuser" },
                    { "label": "App Registration (Client Secret) On-Behalf-Of", "value": "clientsecret-obo" },
                    { "label": "Entra Password (AD Password)", "value": "ad-password" }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.azureCloud",
            "key": "azureCloud",
            "section": "azureCredentials",
            "label": "Azure Cloud",
            "valueType": "string",
            "target": "jsonData",
            "dependsOn": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret-obo'",
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Target Azure cloud environment. Canonical cloud identifiers are defined in [`grafana-azure-sdk-go/azsettings/clouds.go`](https://github.com/grafana/grafana-azure-sdk-go/blob/main/azsettings/clouds.go): `AzureCloud`, `AzureChinaCloud`, `AzureUSGovernment`, `AzureCustomizedCloud`."
            },
            "ui": {
                "component": "select",
                "allowCustom": true,
                "options": [
                    { "label": "Azure", "value": "AzureCloud" },
                    { "label": "Azure China", "value": "AzureChinaCloud" },
                    { "label": "Azure US Government", "value": "AzureUSGovernment" },
                    { "label": "Azure (customized)", "value": "AzureCustomizedCloud" }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.tenantId",
            "key": "tenantId",
            "section": "azureCredentials",
            "label": "Directory (tenant) ID",
            "valueType": "string",
            "target": "jsonData",
            "dependsOn": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret-obo'",
            "requiredWhen": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret-obo'",
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Microsoft Entra (Azure AD) directory (tenant) ID of the app registration. Stored at `jsonData.azureCredentials.tenantId`."
            },
            "validations": [
                {
                    "type": "pattern",
                    "pattern": "^([0-9a-fA-F]{8}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{12})?$",
                    "message": "Tenant ID is required"
                }
            ],
            "ui": {
                "component": "input",
                "placeholder": "XXXXXXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXXXXXXXXXX"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.clientId",
            "key": "clientId",
            "section": "azureCredentials",
            "label": "Application (client) ID",
            "valueType": "string",
            "target": "jsonData",
            "dependsOn": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret-obo' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'ad-password'",
            "requiredWhen": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret-obo' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'ad-password'",
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Microsoft Entra (Azure AD) application (client) ID of the app registration. Stored at `jsonData.azureCredentials.clientId`."
            },
            "validations": [
                {
                    "type": "pattern",
                    "pattern": "^([0-9a-fA-F]{8}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{12})?$",
                    "message": "Client ID is required"
                }
            ],
            "ui": {
                "component": "input",
                "placeholder": "XXXXXXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXXXXXXXXXX"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.azureClientSecret",
            "key": "azureClientSecret",
            "label": "Client Secret",
            "valueType": "string",
            "target": "secureJsonData",
            "dependsOn": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret-obo'",
            "requiredWhen": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret' || azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientsecret-obo'",
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Client secret of the app registration. Stored in `secureJsonData.azureClientSecret`; the legacy key `clientSecret` is preserved for backward compatibility but new datasources should use `azureClientSecret`."
            },
            "ui": {
                "component": "input",
                "placeholder": "XXXXXXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXXXXXXXXXX"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.certificateFormat",
            "key": "certificateFormat",
            "section": "azureCredentials",
            "label": "Format",
            "description": "Choose the format of the certificate (PEM certificates should be in plain text PEM format, PFX certificates should be in base64 encoded PFX format)",
            "valueType": "string",
            "target": "jsonData",
            "dependsOn": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate'",
            "requiredWhen": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate'",
            "validations": [
                {
                    "type": "allowedValues",
                    "values": [
                        "pem",
                        "pfx"
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "ui": {
                "component": "select",
                "options": [
                    { "label": "PEM", "value": "pem" },
                    { "label": "PFX", "value": "pfx" }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.clientCertificate",
            "key": "clientCertificate",
            "label": "Client Certificate",
            "valueType": "string",
            "target": "secureJsonData",
            "dependsOn": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate'",
            "requiredWhen": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate'",
            "validations": [
                {
                    "type": "pattern",
                    "pattern": "^.+$",
                    "message": "Client certificate is required"
                }
            ],
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Client certificate body. For `pem` format, paste the plain-text PEM contents; for `pfx`, paste the base64-encoded PFX bundle. Stored in `secureJsonData.clientCertificate`."
            },
            "ui": {
                "component": "textarea",
                "placeholder": "-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.privateKey",
            "key": "privateKey",
            "label": "Private Key",
            "valueType": "string",
            "target": "secureJsonData",
            "dependsOn": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate' && azure_sdk_settings.certificateFormat == 'pem'",
            "requiredWhen": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate' && azure_sdk_settings.certificateFormat == 'pem'",
            "validations": [
                {
                    "type": "pattern",
                    "pattern": "^.+$",
                    "message": "Private key is required"
                }
            ],
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Private key paired with the PEM client certificate. Stored in `secureJsonData.privateKey`. Only required when `certificateFormat == 'pem'`."
            },
            "ui": {
                "component": "textarea",
                "placeholder": "-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.certificatePassword",
            "key": "certificatePassword",
            "label": "Certificate Password",
            "valueType": "string",
            "target": "secureJsonData",
            "dependsOn": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'clientcertificate' && azure_sdk_settings.certificateFormat == 'pfx'",
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Password protecting the PFX client certificate bundle. Stored in `secureJsonData.certificatePassword`. Only used when `certificateFormat == 'pfx'`."
            },
            "ui": {
                "component": "input",
                "placeholder": "XXXXXXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXXXXXXXXXX"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.userId",
            "key": "userId",
            "section": "azureCredentials",
            "label": "User ID",
            "valueType": "string",
            "target": "jsonData",
            "dependsOn": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'ad-password'",
            "requiredWhen": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'ad-password'",
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Microsoft Entra user principal name used for `ad-password` (Resource Owner Password Credentials) authentication. Stored at `jsonData.azureCredentials.userId`. Not rendered by the Azure Monitor ConfigEditor today; included so consumers of the pack that opt into Entra password auth get the field."
            },
            "ui": {
                "component": "input",
                "placeholder": "user@contoso.onmicrosoft.com"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.password",
            "key": "password",
            "label": "Password",
            "valueType": "string",
            "target": "secureJsonData",
            "dependsOn": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'ad-password'",
            "requiredWhen": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'ad-password'",
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Password used for `ad-password` (Resource Owner Password Credentials) authentication. Stored in `secureJsonData.password`."
            },
            "ui": {
                "component": "input"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.serviceCredentialsEnabled",
            "key": "serviceCredentialsEnabled",
            "section": "azureCredentials",
            "label": "Service Credentials",
            "description": "Choose if fallback service credentials are enabled or disabled for this data source",
            "valueType": "boolean",
            "target": "jsonData",
            "defaultValue": false,
            "dependsOn": "azure_sdk_settings.authType == 'currentuser'",
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Rendered inside the **Fallback Service Credentials** section of the Azure Monitor ConfigEditor when `authType == 'currentuser'`. User-based authentication does not inherently support Grafana features that issue requests without a signed-in user (for example alerting); enabling this provides fallback credentials for those flows. Note: features like alerting will be restricted to the access level of the fallback credentials rather than the user."
            },
            "ui": {
                "component": "radio",
                "options": [
                    { "label": "Enabled", "value": true },
                    { "label": "Disabled", "value": false }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "azure_sdk_settings.oauthPassThru",
            "key": "oauthPassThru",
            "label": "Forward OAuth Identity",
            "valueType": "boolean",
            "target": "jsonData",
            "role": "auth.forwardOAuthToken.enabled",
            "defaultValue": false,
            "help": {
                "markdown": "Forward the signed-in user's OAuth token to Azure when making requests. Stored at `jsonData.oauthPassThru`. Not rendered as a standalone control by the Azure Monitor ConfigEditor; included for plugins that expose it directly."
            },
            "ui": {
                "component": "switch"
            }
        }
    ]
}
